A miniblog api service program that stores data using couchdb instead of relational databases. front end is in python wsgi

= Set up =
== Dependancies ==
 * python
 * erlang language
 * couchdb, some old version may not work, I installed it from svn trunk
 * simplejson
 * eventlet, optional, but necessary if you want to run it as standalone server
 * flup, optional, only required when you run it as a fcgi daemon

== Run it == 
 * start couchdb 
{{{
 % couchdb -b  
}}}
 * run api server
{{{
 % cd $SERVER_INSTALL_DIR
 % ./httpd.py
}}}